'phags pa'i nor bdun|(1) Faith (sŕaddhā, {dad pa}), (2) moral discipline (śīla, {tshul khrims}), (3) hearing (śruta, {thos pa}), (4) generosity (tyāga, {gtong ba}), (5) a sense of shame (hrī, {ngo tsha shes pa}), (6) dread of blame (āpatrāpya, {khrel yod pa}), (7) wisdom (prajñā, {shes rab}) (Rigzin 271).
