gleng gzhi|As one of the twelve aspects of the Dharma, it means the introductions to teachings.\nSee also “twelve wheels of the Dharma.”
gleng gzhi|The introductory sections of a sūtra. Literally it can mean “cause.” One of the nine aspects of the Dharma according to this sūtra. More commonly there are said to be twelve that include these nine.
