sgyu rtsal drug cu rtsa bzhi|The sixty-four crafts, as enumerated in the Mahā vyutpatti, comprise the thirty designated arts, the eighteen requisites of musical performance, the seven harmonious tones of the musical scale, and the nine dramatic moods.\nSee https://read.84000.co/translation/UT22084-031-002.html#UT22084-031-002-2129 .
