zla ba'i bla ma|(1) Name of the thus-gone one of the world system Endowed with Moon. (2) Name of the world system of the thus-gone one Overwhelming with Golden Light.
zla ba'i blo gros|A king.
zla ba'i blo gros|Candrabuddhi (Moon-Like Intellect) is a buddha who inhabits a buddhafield. In http://read.84000.co/translation/toh44-37.html#UT22084-036-008-60 his buddhafield is named Color of the Mirror Disk, and in http://read.84000.co/translation/toh104.html#UT22084-048-004-73 it is named Ādarśa maṇḍala cakra nirghoṣā.
